'''Orr-Om''' was an [[City-ship/Legends|orbital city]] on [[Duro/Legends|Duro]].

==History==
During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], the [[Extragalactic/Legends|extra-galactic]] [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Battle of Duro (Yuuzhan Vong War)|assaulted]] Orr-Om with a serpentine bioengineered monster known as the [[Ychna]]. [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Anakin Solo]] managed to destroy the Ychna, though it was too late for Orr-Om which crashed into the surface of Duro. It was brought out of orbit by [[dovin basal]]s, as were many other orbital cities.

